Class IVarAbstraction

  • java.lang.Object
    • soot.jimple.spark.geom.geomPA.IVarAbstraction
  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    Direct Known Subclasses:
    DummyNode, FullSensitiveNode, HeapInsNode, PtInsNode

    public abstract class IVarAbstraction
extends Object
implements Numberable
    Pointer/object representation in geomPTA. This interface defines the operations needed for manipulating a pointer/object.

    xiao
